{"tid":2368750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋人]  [陸陸雞煲][一日三餐][泰記壽紙網店](前)員工借錢後失蹤","createTime":"2021-01-16T12:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T11:16:17.000Z","uid":37738,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d2f24e65108c625789009732920222434ab109b1","tid":2368750,"uid":37738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:42:08.000Z","msg":"失蹤人士: 李文聰 Lee Man Chung<br />\n年齡: 23<br />\n性別: 男<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2021年1月初開始失蹤，不論telegram, Facebook, 電話等都無法聯繫到佢<br />\n<br />\n先前於陸陸雞煲任職，但陸陸雞煲表示佢已經好耐無番工。<br />\n佢失蹤前報稱現於一日三餐及泰記壽紙網店任職，我地有試過到一日三餐搵佢，<br />\n但可能時間不合未能搵到佢<br />\n<br />\n失聯前曾向不同朋友借錢，原因係屋企需要交保險費(HK$24640.93)。<br />\n借錢其間佢自願影低身份證及相作證明係佢本人借錢<br />\n其後佢都多次表示會每個月慢慢還，但直至現時一次都無還過。<br />\n暫時我地統計到佢借了不同人大約HK$50000 左右<br />\n<br />\n雖然數目唔算大，但對於岩岩FG出黎做野又要養家嘅人黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n借幾千蚊比佢已經好大負擔<br />\n希望大家有佢消息可以提供一下, thanks.<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你都借左錢比佢，請留下TG 我地會盡快聯絡你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n在岩岩我地發現佢已經del了facebook"},{"pid":"03d1729e4cddd42cc505f76dd2ee2f88813f6a9e","tid":2368750,"uid":37738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:42:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30d23093f66524faa4b90f5031f8e78794ce4a22","tid":2368750,"uid":37738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:43:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfc8f53eb237d833a45f18dd7e213390f8216637","tid":2368750,"uid":37738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:43:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6b157fab0e448a684fb744e13117f3a689e3d15","tid":2368750,"uid":37738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:43:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05a0491c2a51bccf136d654eb204c015a17f685f","tid":2368750,"uid":37738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re